data.description: Well Maintained Home in a Well Established neighborhood. This 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath 2,356SF home will not disappoint. Featuring a spacious living room, and nice sized kitchen with lots of natural light. Primary Bedroom features a magnificent on suite bathroom with jacuzzi tub. 3 decent sized bedrooms perfect for any growing family. Situated on an oversized Corner lot, there is plenty of outdoor space for entertaining. As an added bonus there is 900SF below grade that has potential to be finished and add even more living space. Sellers offering a 5K sellers concession to go towards upgrades the buyers may want or willing to work with buyers on a concession for a 2/1 Rate buy down. They offers apply to acceptable offers only.
